A <<.def "filter expression">> is the outermost level of the [[filter syntax|Filter Syntax]]. It consists of optional filter run [[prefix|Filter Run Prefix]] and a filter [[run|Filter Run]]. Multiple filter runs are separated by [[whitespace|Filter Whitespace]].

The first run usually has //no// filter run prefix

<$railroad text="""
\start none
{  (
     - |
     : [[<"prefix">|"Filter Run Prefix"]]
   )
   [[run|"Filter Run"]]  
   +  [[whitespace|"Filter Whitespace"]]
}
"""/>

